
This repository contains the code for simulating 
"Phase change in an opinion-dynamics model with separation of time scales"
described in PHYSICAL REVIEW E 83, 016111 (2011)
Authors: Gerardo In ̃igue1 Ja ́nos Kerte 1,2 Kimmo K. Kai,1 and R. A. Bar

To run it just type:

./opinion 

Options:
-N: number of agents in the ring (default 10)
-T: number of interchange processes (default 10)
-g: number of Euler steps applied (default 10)
-m: neighbours considered (default 1)
-t: dt parameter (default 0.0001)
-f: disables the interchange process (it doesn't take any input) 

